description: Schultheis White, P.C., was founded by attorneys Mark Schultheis and Patrick White. Prior to founding Schultheis White, Mark and Patrick were partners at Iowa's largest law firm. Schultheis White, P.C., is located in Des Moines and represents clients throughout the state of Iowa. Together, Mark and Patrick have over 50 years of experience representing businesses and individuals in commercial litigation, personal injury litigation, and administrative law. They have aggressively and successfully represented clients in dozens of trials, administrative proceedings, and appeals.
